{"tid":505330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[即時] 樂視香港申請清盤！","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T04:55:10.000Z","uid":158504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3bb90e33bf3893b8cf951952e1e08eb25e9bd7","tid":505330,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"樂視香港申請清盤<br />\n文章日期：2017年12月21日 11:40<br />\n<br />\n法庭文件顯示，樂視香港已入紙申請清盤。<br />\n<br />\n內地網絡巨頭樂視自2015年攻港，在香港成立LeSports HK樂視體育。其後投得香港英超及NBA (於OTT平台) 等賽事之獨家播映權。不過，近期多次傳出資金鏈斷裂，今次樂視香港申請清盤，未知英超轉播權會否受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n今年11月，樂視體育出售世界盃播映權予電盈（0008）旗下的nowtv及viutv，至本月初則傳出樂視體育裁員200人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1513827983570&amp;issue=20171221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1513827983570%26issue%3D20171221&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZG9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=840e90f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1513827983570&amp;issue=20171221</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32de6b7d0c64d31d57e8add90192084f8bda8853","tid":505330,"uid":26150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 無咁大個頭又要戴咁大頂帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cef0356b0fd7d3eb3759861a99ab04007d5892","tid":505330,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"支爆近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}